Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your real name is Mr. Reinhard Biermann...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a special orphanage\Nin East Germany, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A testing site to scientifically correct\Nthe children's personalities...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the director there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that place in old East Berlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Kinderheim 511?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.99,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,200)\pos(354,362)}Ghosts of 511
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Mr. Petrov!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're both a psychologist and a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, your specialty in the Ministry of Domestic\NAffairs was personality programming...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a form of brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was a brainwashing expert appointed\Nto a mere orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was just to raise the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there must've been others who were better suited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hide them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The records of the experimental\Nresults from Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hear all the rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the location of the numerous top secret documents\Nfrom East Germany after the Berlin Wall came down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to one theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were being transported to the Soviet\NUnion by train via Romania, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unfortunately, a revolution took place there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the political power of Ceausescu crumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the documents were lost, never to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that's what happened\Nto the documents regarding 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For scholars...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,research thesis and data are more\Nimportant than their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't let them go that easily, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would really like you to show me those documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to accomplish at Kinderheim 511?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the experiment a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fun to manipulate people like guinea pigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a failure, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinderheim 511 was destroyed by a fire in 1985.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:05:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the rumors, the children\Nof the facility killed each other...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had already been relieved of my duty as the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your successor was the first\None killed during that rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of thing wouldn't have\Nhappened if I had been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The experiment was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That during your term of office,\Nthe experiment was going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,although it is said that all documents regarding\NKinderheim 511 were burned back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like the experimental\Ndata from your term in office...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,still remains intact right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're treading on dangerous ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be held responsible if anything happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really afraid or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accompany you until I discover the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever show your face around me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came looking for you because you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your hands out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's living the rest of his life surrounded by\Nhis grandsons, and he leads a calm life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who did such horrible things to children...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have something from Mr. Petrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petrov?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although that corner room has a terrible view...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's pretty convenient at times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already had a dangerous run-in this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some weird men came to my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they your grandsons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a quiet and relaxing retirement,\Nfree from worldly cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a news reporter in old East Germany,\NI couldn't even fathom a lifestyle like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a freelance journalist right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a socialist society, you couldn't\Neven think about being free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being free is good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can follow you around as long as I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've followed you ever since you left your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a magnificent house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rooms looked pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rent is fairly high, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spend the entire day sitting at a cafe\Nand taking walks with your grandsons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you aren't working\Nnow, this is your lifestyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your money coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Data from your failed experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it fetch a good price?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it would sell for even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... leave me alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takes his grandsons to watch a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then they have a chocolate parfait at the cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're different children again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,five, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mr. Petrov's residence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my Cod...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing... the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's conducting the same experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he was still conducting the experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the red-light district at the\Nborder between here and Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These children were born there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right after the Berlin Wall came down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are those who were abandoned\Nbecause of poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gathered children like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are continuing your experiment\Nfrom Kinderheim 511 here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Petrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he your guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:37.77,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,33)}[Editor's note: Icnedliky = dumplings]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like knedliky for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone loves your knedliky, Ana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing my experiment from Kinderheim 511, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said it many times already, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the experiment there was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to continue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that the educational program I created...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would definitely nurture a wonderful personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Educational...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of that was educational?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just human experimentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is education?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't education meant to create a\Nperson that conforms to society?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of education must be administered...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to create a human being that meets society's demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Education is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that an advanced educational\Nsystem was established there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after you've done such horrible things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horrible things?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about what you've done to the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just an idealist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act as though you know everything\Njust because you did some research!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that the incident where\Nthe children killed each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was also a result of your experiment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was something that occurred after\NI was relieved as the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It occurred because an unexpected factor\Nwas introduced into the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpected... factor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nihilism...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destructive impulses...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all things that can control human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, Kinderheim 511 was possessed by them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to the appearance of a young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that you're not responsible for that, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've said many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the experiment was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a common trait among everyone\Nwho came out of Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cannot love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make an interesting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, that's all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't intrude on me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Czech Republic is a democratic country now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll report you to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the right to manage\Nan orphanage in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is unapproved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I file a report, you'll be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for not reporting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you want me to hand over my experimental data to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the deal you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's play soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.56,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going out to play soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov wanted to make a deal with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for your sakes, his deal means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I report this to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys will be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys want to leave that house, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more freedom outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister! The ball's coming your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though they're truly having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you were trying to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Ana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Mrs. Ana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ahold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this to you, Mr. Petrov?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bleeding, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you were trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Key...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Key and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,card...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The PIN...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of my third drawer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the safety deposit box...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is my experimental data and a tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an interview... of a young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By administering hypnosis... and prescribing drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we made him speak about his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the monster that led Kinderheim 511...\Ndown the path of destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were these kids... lacking anything...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were administering education that was totally\Ndifferent from that of Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nihilism...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destructive impulses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to create a person who wouldn't\Nbe engulfed by darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does one do that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a brand new discovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Petrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a perfectly normal, natural thing\Nthat a parent gives to his children...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.61,0:22:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:30.93,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:44.36,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:44.36,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:47.32,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:23:01.00,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:23:01.00,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:25.86,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:34.28,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:36.74,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
